---
title: Bacon-Wrapped Steaks with Mashed Potatoes, Maple-Dijon Brussels Sprouts and Ranch
description: It's hard to beat a beautifully seared steak, but bacon is a good place to start! Pair that with delicious creamy mash and Brussels sprouts, then top it all off with cheesy dill ranch that is truly out of this world, this Fresh Special recipe is destined to please!
